		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:22px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</p>
			<p>As you told us you're interested in NCS, we wanted to introduce ourselves.  We are The Challenge and we are running NCS in your area this summer. We have tried to contact you to tell you more about NCS but haven't managed to speak to you yet.</p>
			<p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="century gothic"><a href="http://youtu.be/YEpX7Q2-CVQ"><img alt="NCS 2014" border="0" height="295" src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images//CCT/It%20all%20starts%20at%20yes.PNG" width="550" /></a></font></p>
			<p>NCS is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to meet new people, make new friends and build the skills and confidence to help you get ahead. Over 120,000 young people have already taken part - don't miss your chance this summer!</p>
			<p><strong>How long does it last?</strong><br>
			<strong>Part 1 - Get Active:</strong> five days (four nights) staying away from home in the countryside doing outdoor adventure activities.<br>
			<strong>Part 2 - Get Involved:</strong> five days (four nights) staying away from home developing skills.<br>
			<strong>Part 3 - Make Your Mark:</strong> community activity days, staying at home at night - four during summer and four on September weekend days.</p>
			<p><strong>Is there a cost?</strong><br>
			Even though each place is valued at over £1000, government backing means NCS costs you no more than a £50 admin fee. Plus, you get an extra £5 discount when you sign up online.</p>
			<p><strong>How do I apply?</strong><br>
			Go to www.NCSTheChallenge.org and use the following unique login details to apply:</p>
			<p><strong>NCS ID: {!Contact.NCS_ID__c}<br>
			Password: {!Contact.Login_PIN__c}</strong></p>
			<p>The website will tell you that some parts need to be completed by your parent or guardian. Please ask them to log in to complete these.<BR><BR>It is quicker to apply online but if your parent or guardian would like a paper copy of the application form instead, please call us on 0203 542 2400 and we’ll send one out in the post. </p>
			<p><strong>Any questions?</strong><br>
			If you have any questions, take a look at&nbsp;<u><a href="http://questions.ncsthechallenge.org/" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 174, 239);" target="_blank">questions.ncsthechallenge.org</a></u>, or get in touch by calling 020 3542 2400 or emailing contact@the-challenge.org.</p>
			<p>Places are filling up fast for this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity so make sure you don't miss out! We'll be in touch once we've received your application.</p>
			<p>Yours sincerely,</p>
			<p>Tanya Dunne<br>
			Head of Customer Services - The Challenge</p></td>
			
